!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
!  Xft settings  !
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

Xft.antialias:  1
Xft.autohint:   0
Xft.dpi:        96
!Xft.dpi:        192
Xft.hinting:    1
Xft.hintstyle:  hintfull
Xft.lcdfilter:  lcddefault
Xft.rgba:       rgb


!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
!  X11 colors settings  !
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

! Colorscheme inspired from gnome-terminal
